close_reason: Coverage thresholds implemented and verified by a PM-recorded full coverage run.
body: "## Discovery\\n\\nVitest reports 95.53% statements, 84.69% branches, 96.36% functions, and 96.1% lines, but vitest.config.ts defines no thresholds. CI therefore uploads coverage without preventing regressions below the documented 90% statement target."
